description.plain: carobae also known as Caroline Baker is a singer/songwriter from Nashville, TN, she is active on the internet since 2011 but has been making music since mid 2019 with her debut single “3am”, her song complatation album “songs for 3am” came out in late 2019 after the album caro released few singles before joining a pop punk band “TRAMP STPAMS” with Marisa Maino and Paige Blue, while in the band caro released her 2 part EPs “The Longest Year: Part One” and “The Longest Year: Part Two” , after her second EP caro didnt upload any music until July 7th with “dead ends/happy endings”, the song marks comeback of carobae and the lead single of her debut album “scared to go to sleep” that came out on November 17, 2022, with 5 singles in total before the album released
